channel.title: The Legend of Zelda: The Windwaker Fan Art
channel.description:
So I was bored and I started playing Zelda again... Then I became obsessed and now I'm playing/drawing Zelda... Made some fan art, and yes I drew it with my mouse because I'ma deprived artist with no tablet. (sadface) Zelda and Link: [img]http://img824.imageshack.us/img824/9273/thelegendofzeldafanart.png[/img]
ProofScrumdiddlies: [img]http://img191.imageshack.us/img191/3594/proofbj.jpg[/img]
Tetra and Zelda (Who are the same people): [img]http://img822.imageshack.us/img822/2368/zeldaandtetrafanart.png[/img]
Proofdiddlydum: [img]http://img8.imageshack.us/img8/500/tetraandzeldafanartproo.jpg[/img]
Hope you like..! Please don't rape my face off. I'm innocent. or whatever.

Thanks Java and maniown(: And Bowser, It’s in a scabbard thing so you can’t actually see the metal of the sword. I realize it looks like a wooden sword… but thats how it’s looked like in all the pictures I looked up, and in the game, so i just went with it. or if you mean Link’s sword, I just suck at coloring metal.
